cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.MM, cs.LG. 

This paper deals with a wireless communication system and its optimization in terms of age of information (AoI). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory). The paper also involves energy harvesting, which suggests the category cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The system is a two-way data exchanging system, which could fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also mentions the use of a smart device, which could be related to cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the paper involves optimization and numerical methods, which could be related to cs.LG (Machine Learning).
